article_text:
Baltic, SD

A Brookings man is dead following a two-vehicle crash on I-29 Friday afternoon, just south of Baltic.

Just before 5 p.m. Friday, the 60-year-old John Lu was rear-ended by another vehicle that had been traveling at a faster speed. The second vehicle had five passengers, four of whom were injured. Three of those injured passengers had serious but non-life-threatening injuries.

The investigation into the accident continues.
